revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}

This template inserts a yellow tick mark (check mark) inline in the text. It is not for use in articles.

This is just a wrapper for {{tlx|tick|color{{=}}yellow}}.

The tick image defaults to 20px in size. To change the size, call with a pixel value as an argument, e.g.: {{tlx|yellow tick|30}}

== See also ==
{{Done/See also}}

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
<!-- ADD CATEGORIES BELOW THIS LINE -->
[[Category:Checkmark insertion templates]]
[[Category:Wikipedia-specific image insertion templates]]
}}</includeonly>

